---
description: User-visible app copy must be English (web UI, API messages shown to users)
globs: apps/web/**/*
alwaysApply: false
---

# English-only user-facing copy

All **user-visible** strings in the web app must be **English**:

- Page titles, headings, body text, labels, placeholders, buttons, links, badges
- Errors, empty states, loading hints, tooltips
- `aria-*` and other accessibility strings shown to users or assistive tech

**OK elsewhere:** repo docs (`README`, notes), migration SQL, internal comments if needed for the team (prefer English in code comments when shared).

When adding or editing UI, write copy directly in English; do not ship Spanish or mixed-language product strings in `apps/web`.
